{"tid":919273,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得draymond green 退步得好快","createTime":"2018-11-28T02:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T19:32:04.000Z","uid":223404,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a495845ab3100a09fb62e12f9a72df90bef1d20","tid":919273,"uid":223404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"15-16年果時進攻係唔差 有jump shoot 有post up   但係自從durant 黎左 見佢拎住個波  進攻已經冇哂威脅咁濟  當年想睇佢一直進步落去 但係呢一兩年打唔番水準。  唔只進攻  防守雖然呢家都算好  但上季同今季都好似已經冇咁硬淨  <br />\n<br />\n講下我對green 睇法   佢真係好獨特 有智慧 有防守 組織好 夠硬淨 又可以打快  現今nba 搵個打4號位有哂佢特質取代佢呢真係好難 有人話佢唔值all star   但除左得分能力 佢真係樣樣有  勇士真係慧眼識英雄   <br />\n<br />\n當年green 進攻high lights <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W3mGrRBZRi0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW3mGrRBZRi0&d=E1T%2B3%2Fwi7mooJkZ6DPK9TbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=162e373c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W3mGrRBZRi0</a>"},{"pid":"2902e17077d0f9caac09f24dacd2bb961d872eb8","tid":919273,"uid":192189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"佢有三分已經夠做, 至斃而家連大空位三分都唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee32b92129ecbe0fedce21c6dfce8287dd84ea0","tid":919273,"uid":214127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"而家咁多人可以攻，留力主力防守仲好啦"},{"pid":"3ddb4a8c1869e73bda94a83b08e6fe1d065ad5cd","tid":919273,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:42:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"150fdf611e827ec7a4c14b99d6dc42c8596ab71a","tid":919273,"uid":65433,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"佢應該係因應球隊需要轉咗打法<br />\n佢係勇士體系入面真係好緊要<br />\n呢排傷咗出唔到你就知佢幾重要"},{"pid":"bc56ebea0338a4090e7268e535c59314be870b66","tid":919273,"uid":204302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ddb4a8c1869e73bda94a83b08e6fe1d065ad5cd","tid":919273,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score"